fr.reflexe.viewshell.api.data.types

Interface IArrayItem

  • All Superinterfaces:
    IDataStructure, Iterable<IData>

    public interface IArrayItem
extends IDataStructure
    Provides access to a single data record managed by an array dataset contained by a parent data structure.

    Thread-safety: implementations of this interface are not required to be safe for concurrent access. Therefore, processing should generally not be shared between multiple threads.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    REFLEXE Technologies

        Gets the data set to which this array item belongs.
